{"commentv2": 1, "number": 3, "id": 192372, "nreplies": 4, "sticky": 0, "user": "89984", "body": "For anyone who cares, he's not easy to solo, at all. hits around 800-1000 each hit on cloth, and has a lot of health. I'd suggest getting a group together, if you want to kill him.", "date": "2007-11-27T17:34:44-06:00", "rating": -2, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "But then again, why would you want to? I guess it's just to say \"I killed Remulos\" because I don't see any other benefit from it.", "creationdate": "2008-04-12T01:36:12-05:00", "id": 30828, "rating": 18, "commentid": 192372, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "TheBeef", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "For those who wonder, killing him make you lose 125 reputation with Cenarion Circle.", "creationdate": "2008-05-24T23:19:55-05:00", "id": 34571, "rating": 19, "commentid": 192372, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Cthu", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Tried to take him out as a resto druid. Wrath spam style. Got him to 20% with innervate/potion cooldowns. EDIT: Had a lot of time on my hands, so just wore him out of mana, used another innervate, and blasted away till he was dead. Screenshot included at top.", "creationdate": "2009-04-30T11:43:26-05:00", "id": 403158, "rating": 1, "commentid": 192372, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Deivijs", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "jeffdebomb, that isnt a guide, i would expect mages to do that without prompting", "creationdate": "2009-08-21T12:07:26-05:00", "id": 421548, "rating": 0, "commentid": 192372, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "255031", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 4, "id": 305633, "nreplies": 2, "sticky": 0, "user": "50728", "body": "He is the youngest of two sons of the demigod Cenarius, and father of Celebras, who trys to rescue his uncle Zaetar's spirit, who was killed in Maraudon by his own offspring, the centaurs.\r\n\r\nRemulos crafted a druidic idol given to Broll Bearmantle which was corrupted by the pit lord Azgalor in the battle for Mount Hyjal. The corrupted idol seemed to be a big source of corruption and had noticeable influence in the Third War, although it was finally cleansed by Broll himself and put to custody by Archdruid Fandral Staghelm in Darnassus.\r\n\r\nThe Cenarion Circle reputation you lose after killing him in-game seems pretty much a symbolic amount, given his importance.", "date": "2008-06-16T02:14:32-05:00", "rating": 29, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "That is not entirely true. The Idol was crafted by Eranikus consort to Ysera. But was only named after Remulos. look it up in the book Stormrage.", "creationdate": "2010-12-22T12:29:36-06:00", "id": 207003, "rating": 1, "commentid": 305633, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Ewonhemer", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "\"The title was perhaps misleading, as the idol did not look at all like the one for whom it was named. Rather, the figurine had been crafted to resemble a rearing green dragon by Remulos.\"", "creationdate": "2015-12-04T11:46:49-06:00", "id": 915744, "rating": 0, "commentid": 305633, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Mordecay", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2008-06-16T02:22:01-05:00", 1, "50728"]}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 5, "id": 559756, "nreplies": 4, "sticky": 0, "user": "CPUzer0", "body": "I kited Remulos all way down to Orgrimmar, took a screenie with him next to thrall, besides that screenie dragging him down there was kinda useless, didn't even get the attention of the crowd really that well. BTW it took pretty long to get him from Moonglade to Orgrimmar! :D", "date": "2009-01-12T16:54:34-06:00", "rating": 3, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "Screenshot or didn't happen!", "creationdate": "2009-01-24T18:19:33-06:00", "id": 75187, "rating": 4, "commentid": 559756, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Rompetomp", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Someone just did this on my server (Stonemaul).  He's engaging him in the Auction House, not really fighting him.  Pretty funny for awhile, but didn't draw a huge crowd or anything.    By the time I switched screens back to WOW he was gone, so no SS here.", "creationdate": "2009-03-02T20:47:36-06:00", "id": 83403, "rating": 2, "commentid": 559756, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "179845", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Posted a screenie, but it will likely be denied. We'll see..  E: In case it wont make it to wowhead, see [url=http://www.filehive.com/files/090607/remulos_orgrimmar.jpg]this[/url] as a proof.", "creationdate": "2009-06-07T09:12:47-05:00", "id": 102420, "rating": 1, "commentid": 559756, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "CPUzer0", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Yeah... Most people dont care about things that arent beating on them... I think its time to show them http://www.wowhead.com/?npc=14503 to see how easy is today's content compared to just a pre-TBC quest ;)", "creationdate": "2009-07-31T09:43:08-05:00", "id": 112903, "rating": 1, "commentid": 559756, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "jjuurriijj", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2009-06-07T09:24:22-05:00", 1, "CPUzer0"]}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 6, "id": 578972, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "307847", "body": "How do you even attack him? Do you have to enter pvp near gaurds attack a dude then kill the gaurds and lower your rep.?", "date": "2009-01-24T19:39:02-06:00", "rating": -2, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "Set your reputation standing with Cenarion Circle to \"at war\".", "creationdate": "2009-01-27T02:24:08-06:00", "id": 75824, "rating": 6, "commentid": 578972, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Caedo", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 7, "id": 583616, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "138326", "body": "I had managed to 1-man him as a level 80 mage. Here are some things you should know\r\n\r\n[b][u]This Guide is for a Level 80 Frost Mage[/u][/b]\r\n[ul]\r\n[li]He will constantly heal himself throughout the fight. Try using [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?spell=30449#taught-by-npc]Spellsteal[/url] in order to get the best of his heals[/li]\r\nThroughout the fight he will cast [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?spell=9758#see-also-ability]Healing Touch[/url] which can not be [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?spell=30449#taught-by-npc]Spellsteal[/url]'d and you are just going to have to make it up.\r\n[li]Make best use of your [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?spell=31687]Summon Water Elemental[/url] spell as well as [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?spell=55342]Mirror Image[/url][/li]\r\nAlso be aware of using  [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?spell=42985]Conjure Mana Gem[/url] during the fight\r\nIf done correctly, you will take him down. for the non believers, check the screenshot page (it might not be uploaded yet) Good luck!\r\n[/ul]", "date": "2009-01-27T14:25:14-06:00", "rating": -5, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
