{"commentv2": 1, "number": 12, "id": 1669429, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "Nebet", "body": "If you look at his idle animation, it looks like he holds his branch-hand up in front of his chest, takes his other hand and pokes the end of one of the branch-fingers, then jerks it away and shakes his hand as if he stuck himself. \"Ooh! Ouch, that hurt!\"\r\n\r\nPretty funny little detail, if you ask me.", "date": "2012-05-21T22:04:21-05:00", "rating": 9, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "I have seen it, tried to grab a screenshot, see if it works. It did. If approved, you will see it in the screenshots tab here.", "creationdate": "2016-09-13T14:23:49-05:00", "id": 977077, "rating": 0, "commentid": 1669429, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Thairalumen", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
